column4: HI. MY COMPUTER DOESN'T WORKS ANYMORE. UBUNTU BROKEN IT. I WANT MY MONEY BACK NOW, MY HARDWARE MEELTED.

as you probably know, this channel is only for ubuntu support.  I understand you're trying to be funny in some strange way, but keep the discussion related to ubuntu support only.  If you want to joke around and have fun, try #ubuntu-offtopic
